         xsi:schemaLocation="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook http://www.docbook.org/xml/5.0/xsd/docbook.xsd">
    <title>Making additions via
        <literal>svn add</literal>
    </title>
    <para>
        You can create new files or directories and add them to the repository via
        <programlisting><![CDATA[
svn add [file/directoryName]            
]]></programlisting>
        In the case where a directory is added, its contents are added recursively also.
    </para>
    <para>
        After the addition command the file has been flagged for addition (visible via <userinput>svn status</userinput>).
        The resources will only be added to the actual repository once the changes are committed.
    </para>
</section>    